description:
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen to join the Integrated Medicine Directorate as a Medical Secretary primarily supporting the Diabetes team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The applicant will need excellent interpersonal skills, be able to communicate with tact and diplomacy, whilst providing a professional and comprehensive secretarial service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You must have the ability to work in a busy environment and be confident in liaising with all grades of healthcare staff and patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post is 22.5 hours per week and based at the University Hospital of Wales.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ability to speak Welsh is desirable for this post; Welsh and/or English speakers are equally welcome to apply.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Closing date: 12th November 2020.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name: Claire Matthews&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title: Directorate Support Manager&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address: claire.matthews@wales.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Telephone number: 02921841223&lt;/p&gt;
